气象学家[[威廉·查尔斯·雷德菲尔德|威廉·雷德菲尔德]]（{{lang|en|William C. Redfield}}）于8月30日在[[佛得角|佛得角]]以南海域发现本季第三号热带风暴，这也是有纪录以来第一个[[佛得角型飓风|佛得角型飓风]]<ref name="Partagas" />。气旋起初朝西北偏西移动并逐渐增强，于9月1日成为飓风。接下来两天里，风暴又有显著强化，于9月2日清晨达到二级飓风标准。9月3日，气旋增强成四级飓风，达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时240公里的最高强度，“赫尔曼号”（{{lang|en|Hermann}}）桅帆船不久后测得低至924[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.3[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的[[气压|气压]]值，创下大西洋飓风最高强度纪录，直到70余年后才被达到[[五级大西洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]标准，气压低至910毫巴（百帕，27英寸汞柱）的[[1924年古巴飓风|1924年古巴飓风]]打破。<ref name="1846pres">{{cite report | author = Jose F. Partagás | year = 1993 | title = Impact on Hurricane History of a Revised Lowest Pressure at Havana (Cuba) During the October 11, 1846 Hurricane | accessdate = 2016-11-05 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/impacthurrhist.pdf | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040631/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/impacthurrhist.pdf | format = PDF | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>虽然[[1846年哈瓦那飓风|1846年哈瓦那飓风]]强度可能更高<ref name="KeysHistory">{{cite report | author = Gail Swanson | author2 = Jerry Wilkinson | url = http://www.keyshistory.org/hurricanelist.html | title = Florida Keys Hurricanes of the Last Millennium | publisher = Historical Preservation Society of the Upper Keys | accessdate = 2016-11-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160623224931/http://www.keyshistory.org/hurricanelist.html | archivedate = 2016-06-23 | date =  }}</ref>，但飓风数据库中的正式纪录是从[[1851年大西洋飓风季|1851年]]开始，所以不计在内<ref name="HURDAT" />。

9月5日，飓风已在蜿蜒向西北前进期间开始减弱。9月7日清晨，气旋转向北上，在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]][[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]以东约550公里海域经过，强度降至三级飓风标准。风暴当天经过[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]近海，<ref name="HURDAT" />外围[[雨带|雨带]]在该州南部沿海地区降下暴雨<ref>{{cite report | url = http://repository.wrclib.noaa.gov/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1002&context=nws_tech_memos | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070311045226/http://repository.wrclib.noaa.gov/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1002&context=nws_tech_memos | archivedate = 2007-03-11 | title = Tropical cyclones affecting North Carolina since 1586: An historical perspective | author = James E. Hudgins | date = 2000-04 | work = [[美国国家气象局|National Weather Service]] | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | page = 11 | accessdate = 2007-03-11 | location = [[黑堡_(弗吉尼亚州)|Blacksburg, Virginia]] | format = PDF | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。9月7日，“阿尔伯马尔号”（{{lang|en|Albermarle}}）双桅船在海上失踪，船上40人之后推定均已溺毙<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlya1.html | title = The Deadliest Atlantic Tropical Cyclones, 1492 – Present | author1 = Edward N. Rappaport | author2 = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | author3 = John L. Beven II | date = 1997-04-22 | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-10-18 | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018034515/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlya1.html | archivedate = 2014-10-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlyappnote.html | title = The Deadliest Atlantic Tropical Cyclones, 1492 – Present: Notes to appendices | author1 = Edward N. Rappaport | author2 = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | author3 = John L. Beven II | date = 1997-04-22 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-10-18 | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018133905/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlyappnote.html | archivedate = 2014-10-18 }}</ref>。风暴回转向[[罗盘方位|东北偏东]]移动并继续稳步消退，到9月9日已减弱成一级飓风。9月10日，气旋中心行进至[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]][[弗洛雷斯岛_(亚速群岛)|弗洛雷斯岛]]西北偏北约845公里洋面，此后便失去踪影。<ref name="HURDAT" />
